      "Title": "MegaForm.Sdk.FormSchemaInfo",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/MegaForm.Sdk.FormSchemaInfo.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A form's schema parsed into typed, read-only field metadata (decoupled from the\ninternal storage models). Returned by <code>ISchemaApi.Parse</code>. Row/column layout is\nflattened so <xref href=\"MegaForm.Sdk.FormSchemaInfo.Fields\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> is the same ordered, input-field list the server\nvalidates against.</p>\n"
    },
