      "Title": "MegaForm.Sdk.IMegaFormClient",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/MegaForm.Sdk.IMegaFormClient.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">The single public entry point for using MegaForm programmatically. Resolve it from\nDI (<code>services.AddMegaFormSdk()</code>) or, in non-DI hosts (e.g. a DNN Razor host),\nvia the ambient <xref href=\"MegaForm\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> accessor.</p>\n"
    },
