      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormClient",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormClient.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Default <xref href=\"MegaForm.Sdk.IMegaFormClient\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> — a thin facade that maps SDK DTOs to/from\nMegaForm.Core repositories. It does NOT contain business logic; it reuses Core.\nTenant/user context comes from the ambient <xref href=\"MegaForm.Core.Interfaces.IPlatformContext\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> (when the\nhost provides one) and can be overridden per call via <xref href=\"MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormScope\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormFileContent.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormFileContent.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormFileContent",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormFileContent.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">The bytes + metadata of a file, ready to stream to a download response.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormScope.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormScope.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormScope",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormScope.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Explicit tenant/user context for an SDK call. Pass this when the caller runs\nOUTSIDE a MegaForm request (background job, scheduler, another module) where the\nambient <code>IPlatformContext</code> is not available or not the right tenant. When\nomitted, the ambient platform context is used.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormSdk.yml",
      "output": {
        ".html": {
          "relative_path": "api/MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormSdk.html"
        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormSdk",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormSdk.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Ambient accessor for hosts that cannot use constructor injection — e.g. a DNN Razor\nhost, a DDR template, or a legacy .ascx. Call <xref href=\"MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormSdk.Initialize(System.IServiceProvider)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> once at host\nstartup with the application's <xref href=\"System.IServiceProvider\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>, then use\n<xref href=\"MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormSdk.RunAsync%60%601(System.Func%7bMegaForm.Sdk.IMegaFormClient%2cSystem.Threading.Tasks.Task%7b%60%600%7d%7d)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> which opens a DI scope, resolves the client, and disposes it.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-csharp\">// DNN razor host:\nvar forms = await MegaFormSdk.RunAsync(c =&gt; c.Forms.ListFormsAsync(\n    new FormQuery { Status = \"published\" },\n    new MegaFormScope { PortalId = PortalSettings.PortalId }));</code></pre>\n<p sourcefile=\"api/MegaForm.Sdk.MegaFormSdk.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"11\">In DI hosts (Oqtane/Web), prefer injecting <xref href=\"MegaForm.Sdk.IMegaFormClient\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> directly.</p>\n"
    },
