      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "MegaForm.Sdk.SubmitResult",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/MegaForm.Sdk.SubmitResult.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Result of submitting form data through <code>ISubmissionApi.SubmitAsync</code>. Mirrors the\nserver submission pipeline's outcome. On a validation failure <xref href=\"MegaForm.Sdk.SubmitResult.Success\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> is\nfalse and <xref href=\"MegaForm.Sdk.SubmitResult.ValidationErrors\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> carries the per-field messages (no row is saved).</p>\n"
    },
